WEBVTT

07:17.145 --> 07:18.855
Your Holiness.

07:19.355 --> 07:21.482
Mother Superion, are you alone?

07:22.608 --> 07:23.693
I am.

07:23.776 --> 07:26.320
I have been researching Adriel.

07:26.404 --> 07:27.363
Tell me.

07:27.947 --> 07:29.449
I can't talk now.

07:29.532 --> 07:32.577
I'm requesting your presence
at a secret conclave in Madrid.

07:32.660 --> 07:36.289
You and everyone else I can still trust.

07:36.998 --> 07:37.832
I'll be there.

07:37.915 --> 07:39.542
All is not lost, Mother.

07:39.625 --> 07:41.335
We shall rely on faith.

32:23.191 --> 32:24.734
Francesco, let's go!

34:59.263 --> 35:03.392
Yes, several of our
guests say they heard gunshots upstairs.
